<h1 style="margin-top:20px">Trump claims First Lady Melania has &#39;gotten to know&#39; Kim Jong Un. She has never met him.</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Not the first time Trump made a false claim.</p>
<div class="publish-info">
<p>
<span class="non-date">
<a href="https://mothership.sg/author/jason-fan"><span class="author-name ">Jason Fan</span></a><span class="pipe">|</span>
</span>
<span class="publish-date">
<img class="clock" src="/assets/images/icons/clock.png" />
August 27, 06:04 PM </span>
</p>
</div>
<div class="social-share ">
<a href="#" class="social-fb-share">
<span><img src="/assets/images/icons/svg/fb-icon.svg" /></span>
</a>
<a href="https://twitter.com/share?text=Trump claims First Lady Melania has &#39;gotten to know&#39; Kim Jong Un. She has never met him.&url=https://mothership.sg/2019/08/trump-melania-met-kim-false/" class="social-tw-share" target="_blank">
